# Designs

## Project-D1 Explorer View & Tree Component
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `frontend/src/views/ExplorerView.vue`, `components/TreeView.vue`
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** Project-A3

- Fetch and display recursive project file tree
- Handle node expand/collapse with chevron animation
- Filter tree client-side by search query
- Render file previews by MIME type (text, image, PDF, download)

- `useProject.ts` for project path and close action
- `TreeNode` type from `@/types/wiki`

